g aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jmi1665702688698.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jmi1665702688698.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jmi1665702688698.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jmi1665702688698\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Static Server Page\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Static Server Page is a Component that defines a web page that is updated as a complete page at runtime.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jmi1665702688698__section_ubc_mc4_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d321304e51\">Characteristics</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"jmi1665702688698__table_d10616e1_d10617e1_d10618e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jmi1665702688698__table_d10616e1_d10617e1_d10618e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jmi1665702688698__table_d10616e1_d10617e1_d10618e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jmi1665702688698__table_d10616e1_d10617e1_d10618e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Icon:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jmi1665702688698__table_d10616e1_d10617e1_d10618e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><img alt=\"Icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"jmi1665702688698__image_xgk_4c4_mwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/component.png?_LANG=enus\"/></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jmi1665702688698__table_d10616e1_d10617e1_d10618e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jmi1665702688698__table_d10616e1_d10617e1_d10618e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">cpt</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jmi1665702688698__table_d10616e1_d10617e1_d10618e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jmi1665702688698__table_d10616e1_d10617e1_d10618e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jmi1665702688698__table_d10616e1_d10617e1_d10618e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Has layout?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jmi1665702688698__table_d10616e1_d10617e1_d10618e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jmi1665702688698__table_d10616e1_d10617e1_d10618e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Layout binding?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jmi1665702688698__table_d10616e1_d10617e1_d10618e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">XHTML tag-based</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jmi1665702688698__table_d10616e1_d10617e1_d10618e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jmi1665702688698__table_d10616e1_d10617e1_d10618e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jmi1665702688698__table_d10616e1_d10617e1_d10618e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jmi1665702688698__table_d10616e1_d10617e1_d10618e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yth1665702550544.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yth1665702550544.html\" title=\"A Component Entity is a Development Object that represents data that is owned by a Component. It is part of the Component’s structure and is maintained as part of the Component, although it may reference and inherit from a Modeled Entity.\">Component Entity</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wyt1665702609153.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wyt1665702609153.html\" title=\"A Label is a Development Object that contains text that appears on a presentation component. Labels have properties, but most cannot be set dynamically.\">Label</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cny1665702550298.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cny1665702550298.html\" title=\"A Code Container is a type of Property that holds code, such as ProcScript, JavaScript, or HTML. It can contain one or more code modules, such as triggers, operations, functions, or entries, or HTML for the layout.\">Code Container</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jmi1665702688698__table_d10616e1_d10617e1_d10618e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jmi1665702688698__table_d10616e1_d10617e1_d10618e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ifc1665702608950.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ifc1665702608950.html\" title=\"A Component is a Main Development Object that defines an executable part of an application. It defines the data structure used to access data, the layout (if applicable) used to present it, and the actions used to modify, validate, and store data.\">Component</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jmi1665702688698__table_d10616e1_d10617e1_d10618e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jmi1665702688698__table_d10616e1_d10617e1_d10618e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jmi1665702688698__table_d10616e1_d10617e1_d10618e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jmi1665702688698__table_d10616e1_d10617e1_d10618e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ird1665702714456.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ird1665702714456.html\" title=\"A Signature is a Development Object that describes the remote interface of a component, or modeled entity operation. Signatures for Uniface components and modeled entity operations are automatically generated, but signatures for non-Uniface components that Uniface can call at runtime, must be explicitly defined.\">Signature</a>, <span class=\"ph filepath\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ServerPageName</var>.usp</span>, <span class=\"ph filepath\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ServerPageName</var>.hts</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jmi1665702688698__table_d10616e1_d10617e1_d10618e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jmi1665702688698__table_d10616e1_d10617e1_d10618e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">usp:<var class=\"keyword varname\">ServerPageName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jmi1665702688698__section_gnk_pc4_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d321304e326\">Specialization</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jmi1665702688698__p_d95675e1_d95676e1_d95677e1\">Static Server Page specializes Component in the following\n        ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"jmi1665702688698__ul_dvd_rc4_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jmi1665702688698__li_d38507e1_d38508e1_d38509e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jmi1665702688698__p_d95678e1_d95679e1_d95680e1\">It has an HTML layout.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jmi1665702688698__li_d38510e1_d38511e1_d38512e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jmi1665702688698__p_d95681e1_d95682e1_d95683e1\">It has specialized triggers.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jmi1665702688698__li_d38513e1_d38514e1_d38515e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jmi1665702688698__p_d95684e1_d95685e1_d95686e1\">Its widgets are HTML controls.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jmi1665702688698__li_d38516e1_d38517e1_d38518e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jmi1665702688698__p_d95687e1_d95688e1_d95689e1\">It uses Uniface-specific XHTML tags to bind the\n            component structure to the layout.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jmi1665702688698__li_d38519e1_d38520e1_d38521e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jmi1665702688698__p_d95690e1_d95691e1_d95692e1\">It compiles to a deployable USP runtime component,\n            and generates associated JavaScript files.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jmi1665702688698__li_d38522e1_d38523e1_d38524e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jmi1665702688698__p_d95693e1_d95694e1_d95695e1\">If the layout is defined as external, it generates an\n            HTML layout file (<span class=\"ph filepath\">.hts</span>).</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jmi1665702688698__section_pjs_rc4_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d321304e378\">Triggers and Operations</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"jmi1665702688698__ul_q3g_tc4_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jmi1665702688698__li_d38525e1_d38526e1_d38527e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hmn1665702683413.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hmn1665702683413.html\" title=\"System trigger that provides component-specific post-processing.\">trigger postActivate</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jmi1665702688698__li_d38528e1_d38529e1_d38530e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"muo1665702683268.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/muo1665702683268.html\" title=\"System trigger that provides component-specific pre-processing. It is required in web applications to recreate the component state.\">trigger preActivate</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jmi1665702688698__li_d38531e1_d38532e1_d38533e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ghq1665702608876.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ghq1665702608876.html\" title=\"Reacts to asynchronous messages that come from outside the application.\">trigger receiveMessage</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"jmi1665702688698__ul_x3g_tc4_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jmi1665702688698__li_d38534e1_d38535e1_d38536e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mkf1719505969039.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mkf1719505969039.html\" title=\"Default component operation, which is invoked by the activate statement.\">operation exec</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jmi1665702688698__li_d38537e1_d38538e1_d38539e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zye1719506814289.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zye1719506814289.html\" title=\"Defines the component behavior when a component instance is created with newinstance (or by activate when newinstance is executed implicitly).\">operation init</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jmi1665702688698__li_d38540e1_d38541e1_d38542e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tcd1719504517290.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tcd1719504517290.html\" title=\"Defines the component behavior when a component instance is removed.\">operation cleanup</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jmi1665702688698__li_d38543e1_d38544e1_d38545e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tdr1719503726176.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tdr1719503726176.html\" title=\"Defines the behavior that should occur in response to an Accept request. If an Accept trigger is defined, it is exposed as the accept operation in the component signature.\">operation accept</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jmi1665702688698__li_d38546e1_d38547e1_d38548e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"icw1719507043571.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/icw1719507043571.html\" title=\"Defines the processing that should occur during a Quit request. If a quit trigger is defined in a component, it is exposed as the quit operation in the component signature.\">operation quit</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613945\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613945\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Static Server Page Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Static Server Page A Static Server Page is a Component that defines a web page that is updated as a complete page at runtime. Characteristics Characteristics Icon: Object type code: cpt Main Development Object? Yes Has layout? Yes Layout binding? XHTML tag-based Part of: — Contains: Component Entity , Label , Property , Code Container Generalization: Component Specializations: — Compilation output: Signature , ServerPageName .usp , ServerPageName .hts URI format: usp: ServerPageName Specialization Static Server Page specializes Component in the following ways: It has an HTML layout. It has specialized triggers. Its widgets are HTML controls. It uses Uniface-specific XHTML tags to bind the component structure to the layout. It compiles to a deployable USP runtime component, and generates associated JavaScript files. If the layout is defined as external, it generates an HTML layout file ( .hts ). Triggers and Operations trigger postActivate trigger preActivate trigger receiveMessage operation exec operation init operation cleanup operation accept operation quit Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}